\v 3 One of the headsВҰ161528 of the sea creature looked as if someone had wounded it so that it had died, butВҰ161523 that wound had healedВҰ161542 and as a result, all the people of the earthВҰ161551 marvelledВҰ161545 at the sea creature and \add obeyed\add* it.
